# DBOT Supply Chain Analytics — Revised Plan

## Key Research Findings

**OCP Solutions** (Casablanca, est. 2018) is the analytics consulting arm of OCP Group (world's largest phosphate producer). Their method is literally called **D-B-O-T: Design → Build → Operate → Transfer** — your project folder name matches exactly.

Their core capabilities from [ocpsolutions.ma](https://ocpsolutions.ma):
1. **Operations Research** — optimization models for scheduling, inventory, distribution
2. **Machine Learning** — classification/prediction for decision support
3. **Industry 4.0 / Digital Transformation** — applied to supply chain

Their flagship achievement (published in [INFORMS](https://informs.org), the world's top OR journal):
- **PSIMVA** = Production Scheduling, Inventory Management & Vessel Assignment
- Method: Mixed-Integer Linear Programming (MILP) + hybrid Benders Decomposition
- Result: **+$240M annual turnover** for OCP Group

---

## What Aligns With Your Data

| Model | Data Fit | OCP Alignment | Verdict |
|---|---|---|---|
| **TOPSIS Supplier Ranking** (OR) | ✅ Strong — 100 suppliers, real costs, real delivery delays | ✅ OR optimization is their core | **Do this** |
| **Late Delivery Risk Classifier** (ML) | ✅ Strongest — 20K rows, labeled target variable | ✅ ML for decision support is their 2nd pillar | **Do this** |
| **Game Theory Pricing** | ❌ No competitor data exists | ⚠️ Not their focus area | **Drop** |
| **Production Scheduling (MILP)** | ⚠️ Lack production capacity data | ✅ This is their flagship | Not feasible with current data |
| **Prescriptive Discount Optimization (OR)** | ✅ Strongest — real prices, COGS, discounts, and quantities | ✅ Hybrid ML + Constrained Optimization is heavily used | **Added (Model C)** |

